&lt;header class="step__head"&gt;&lt;p class="step__title"&gt;Wait for metrics to be computed&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/header&gt;
&lt;div class="step__body"&gt;&lt;p&gt;Looking at the log trace, we can see that metrics are being computed for our traces:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;figure class="figure"&gt;
 &lt;div class="figure__inner"&gt;
